li>Felix Julie, JHU: <em>Black hole binaries in Einstein-scalar-Gauss-Bonnet gravity.<\/em><\/li>\n<li>Andrea Antonelli, JHU: <em>Noisy neighbours: inference biases from overlapping gravitational-wave signals.<\/em><\/li>\n<li>Thomas Helfer, JHU: <em>[Various NR stuff]<\/em><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n<h4>Another time<\/h4>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Nicola Giacobbo, BHAM: <em>[Accretion disks around SMBH, Bardeen-Petterson effect]<\/em><\/li>\n<li>Nick Speeney, JHU: <em>[Dark matter profiles around massive BHs]<\/em><\/li>\n<li>Zipeng Wang, JHU: <em>[Plasma-induced superradiance around black holes]<\/em><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n<h2>Slides<\/h2>\n\n<p>Please dump your slides in this git repository (go to \"Add files\", then \"Upload files\"):<\/p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/github.com\/dgerosa\/HopBham-workshop\">github.com\/dgerosa\/HopBham-workshop<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n\n<h2>Here we are<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"616\" src=\"https:\/\/davidegerosa.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/hopbham-1024x616.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3833\" srcset=\"https:\/\/davidegerosa.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/hopbham-1024x616.png 1024w, https:\/\/davidegerosa.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/hopbham-300x180.png 300w, https:\/\/davidegerosa.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/hopbham-768x462.png 768w, https:\/\/davidegerosa.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/hopbham.png 1522w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Check me out on&nbsp;github.com\/dgerosa\/pdetclassifier. Here we are<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":3783,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_coblocks_attr":"","_coblocks_dimensions":"","_coblocks_responsive_height":"","_coblocks_accordion_ie_support":"","amp_status":"","spay_email":""},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/davidegerosa.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\